nomadcap (0.5-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Fix VLAN capture: match and parse 802.1Q tagged frames (--vlan).
  * Fix IEEE OUI loader: row indexing, cache bounds, allocation checks.
  * Add -a/--announce to nomadcap6 for unsolicited neighbor advertisements.
  * Validate -n, -m, and -d command line arguments.
  * Use 24-hour clock in ISO 8601 timestamps.
  * Harden packet parsing against truncated captures.
  * Improved interface auto-selection in both tools.
  * Shared common and syslog modules between nomadcap and nomadcap6.
  * Build with -Wall -Wextra -O2; warning and memory leak cleanup.

 -- Jonathan Cormier <jonathan@cormier.co>  Thu, 11 Jun 2026 18:51:13 -0300

nomadcap (0.4-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * IPv6 support in nomadcap6.
  * Syslog support for nomadcap and nomadcap6.
  * VLAN filtering.
  * Long options support.
  * Additional scripts: block_mac.sh, slack.sh.
  * Pass device name to exec scripts.
  * Improved interface selection logic.
  * Dockerfile for containerized builds.

 -- Jonathan Cormier <jonathan@cormier.co>  Wed, 18 Mar 2026 13:27:00 -0300

